    "title": "Send/Transactions Tab Font Inconsistencies on macOS",
    "body": "Master built on macOS 10.15.7 and Qt 5.15.1 shows font inconsistencies as highlighted by the below screenshots:\r\n![mac-os-resize](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/23396902/98743568-46773100-237e-11eb-9ce2-4f562eb88880.png)\r\nUnder the `Send` tab the `Pay To` field has a noticeably smaller font than the `Label` field. Additionally under the `Transactions` Tab, the word \"All\" looks bad as the A and L are very close together.\r\n\r\nThese inconsistencies are not showing up with master built on Arch Linux (Kernel 5.18.5) and Qt 5.15.1:\r\n![linux-resize](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/23396902/98743994-f5b40800-237e-11eb-9aa3-cf39fc1385ad.png)\r\n",
