      "body": "> Under the `Send` tab the `Pay To` field has a noticeably smaller font than the `Label` field.\r\n\r\nThis is caused by the `.AppleSystemUIFontMonospaced` font, which is chosen by Qt.\r\n\r\n> Additionally under the `Transactions` Tab, the word \"All\" looks bad as the A and L are very close together.\r\n\r\nIt is very similar to #235. It does not looks like we could solve it effectively.\r\n",
